data.description: PRICE IMPROVEMENT! GREAT LOCATION!! This beautiful 4 bedroom & 2 bathroom Sanibel Model smart home located in the desirable community of BARBADOS AT OASIS. This home is perfect for a family or anyone who needs the extra space.This home has a one car garage, that provides convenient parking and storage.The backyard and patio has plenty of space that's great for entertaining guests or relaxing outdoors.Very safe gated community with aclubhouse, community pool, playground, fitness center, and green spaces.BARBADOS AT OASIS is just minutes away from Baptist Hospital, Florida Turnpike, shopping center, restaurants, and Air Force Base. This is a convenient location with easy access to everything you need.Just like new built in 2019!
